title: DJ Fatal Presents Tupac - The Unheard, The Scrapped and The Remi

05. 2Pac ft. Nuttso - Ghetto Star (DJ Fatal Remix)
06. Nuttso & Lil' Big - Don't Sleep (DJ Fatal Remix)
07. 2Pac ft. Kurupt and Daz Dillinger - Don't Go 2 Sleep (DJ Fatal Extended Female Remix)
08. 2Pac ft. Patti Labelle - Can U Get Away (DJ Fatal Remix)
09. 2Pac ft. Foster The People - Nothing To Lose (DJ Fatal Remix)
